    "description": "<strong>为什么爱总会让人受伤？</strong><br><strong>为何情人总分分合合？</strong><br><strong>每段感情都有保质期？</strong><br><strong>情人在分手边缘是否总免不了终极对决？</strong><br><strong>你听过的最奇葩的分手理由是什么？</strong><br><strong>你是否有揍对方一顿的冲动？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/6e881462311d8da86ab0cb818722d5a9.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>《分手擂台》将满足您所有的疑问与幻想。表面上这是一款暴力血腥的清版动作游戏，实质上是一款探索情感的成长游戏。这款独特的清版格斗游戏，打破传统格斗街机的局限，让您与前任们来一场别开生面的对决。游戏独树一帜之处在于其丰富的故事情节，将激烈的战斗与深刻的情感无缝结合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《分手擂台》中，您将探索并表达亲密关系中的种种冲突与情感。游戏的终极目的是自我觉醒，每一次分手，不仅仅是与他人的分离，更是与过去的自己告别。这是每一个经历过分手的人必须学习经历的重要一课。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>加入我们的情感探索，通过这场独特而引人入胜的游戏体验，找到内心的平静与成长之路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>**注意：**本游戏剧情略显浮夸与荒诞，旨在表现和探索人生的荒诞性。作者在冲突矛盾的表达上采用了夸张的剧情手法，不具有现实参考意义。<br><br>踏上《分手擂台》的情感旅程，接受挑战，释放压力，让我们一起迎接爱的终极对决！",
